      <title>德克萨斯州收费公路收购将使纳税人损失至少 17 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/texas-tollroad-takeover-to-cost-taxpayers-at-least-1-7-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德克萨斯州计划终止 52 年的收费公路特许权并恢复国家控制，这将使纳税人损失至少 17 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/texas-tollroad-takeover-to-cost-taxpayers-at-least-1-7-billion</guid>
